headline: How to Play NextEra Energy Stock After Q1 Earnings Beat
summary: NEE continues to gain from the decline in interest rates, low-cost strategically located assets, and increasing clean energy generation capacity to meet demand from its expanding customers.

headline: NextEra: A Strong Q1, Shares Now Undervalued, Upgrading To Buy
